<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>1. Con la etiqueta <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;script&gt;</code> al final del <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;body&gt;</code></strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">En tu <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">index.html</code>, la última línea antes de <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;/body&gt;</code> es:</p>
<div class="relative group/copy bg-bg-000/50 border-0.5 border-border-400 rounded-lg"><div class="sticky opacity-0 group-hover/copy:opacity-100 top-2 py-2 h-12 w-0 float-right"><div class="absolute right-0 h-8 px-2 items-center inline-flex z-10"><button class="inline-flex
