 token" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133);">button</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133);"> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(240, 117, 128);">id</span><span class="token token attr-equals" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">=</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">"</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">run-btn</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">"</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">&gt;</span><span>▶ Ejecutar</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">&lt;/</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133);">button</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
