class="token token property-access" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">addEventListener</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">(</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">"click"</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">,</span><span> runCode</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">)</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">;</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token template-punctuation" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">`</span><span class="token token template-punctuation" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">`</span><span class="token token template-punctuation" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">`</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">
</span></span><span>
</span><span>---
</span><span>
</span><span>**El flujo completo es:**
</span><span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);"></span><span class="token token template-punctuation" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">`</span><span class="token token template-punctuation" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">`</span><span class="token token template-punctuation" style="color: rgb(155, 233, 99);">`</span><span>
</span></span><span><span>index</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">.</span><span class="token token property-access">html</span><span> → carga → style</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">.</span><span class="token token property-access" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">css</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">(</span><span>estilos</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">)</span><span>
</span></span><span><span>           → carga → app</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">.</span><span class="token token property-access" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">js</span><span>    </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">(</span><span>lógica</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">)</span><span>
</span></span><span>                       ↓
</span><span>              busca elementos por id
</span><span>                       ↓
</span><span><span>              agrega </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(112, 184, 255);">eventos</span><span> </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">(</span><span>clicks</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">,</span><span> etc</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">.</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">)</span><span>
</span></span><span>                       ↓
</span><span><span>              manipula el </span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">DOM</span><span> cuando el usuario interactúa</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">En resumen: <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">&lt;script src="app.js"&gt;</code> conecta los archivos, y los <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">id</code> son el puente entre el HTML y el JS para identificar cada elemento.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
